    "steam_appid": 3040820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040820/extras/e496e576ab87b77926c1635ccde2f5a8.avif?t=1771525657\" width=630 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Kitties Memories is an exciting 2D hidden object game with handcrafted graphics where you search for lost souls of kitties in a surreal, fantasy world. As you find each lost soul, it transforms into a normal kitty that you must discover again. Each encounter allows you to unlock and relive its favorite memory with its human in life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3040820/extras/14e6df37ef78682089bcb67b733e619f.avif?t=1771525657\" width=630 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Unique Gameplay: </strong>Discover lost souls of kitties and help them remember their favorite memories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Handcrafted Graphics:</strong> Beautiful, intricate illustrations create a surreal and engaging environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Interactive Elements: </strong>Interact with various objects to reveal hidden souls.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Symbol Collections: </strong>Find and complete collections of mysterious symbols, adding an extra layer of intrigue to your journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Immersive Experience: </strong>Enjoy a relaxing yet challenging game that combines hidden object mechanics in a narrative way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Auto-Save:</strong> Auto-save feature ensures players' progress is saved automatically, allowing uninterrupted play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Achievements: </strong> A range of achievements, including 9 hidden ones.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Music: </strong> Relaxing and immersive soundtrack that perfectly matches the pace of the game.</p></li></ul>",
